<p>I&#8217;ll post my slides of dubious value later today or tomorrow at the <a href="http://web.zen.si">usual place</a> and I&#8217;ll try to prepare a Lessig-like webcast over the weekend. I hope to see everyone next week on Tuesday. Bo≈°tjan Ber??i?? will talk about responsibility of publishers on web, a talk that everyone who publishes on the web in Slovenia should probably hear.</p>
